snippet.title: Tomay Hrid Majhare Rakhbo ( হৃদ মাঝারে ) ft. Anusheh Anadil | Coke Studio Bangla Song 2016

localized.description:
Coke Studio Bangla Presents Bangla Folk Sad Song " tomay hrid majhare rakhbo chere debo na studio Song " sung by Anusheh Anadil.

Tomay Hrid Majhare Rakhibo Chere Debona is  a Bengali Traditional Folk Song written by Dwij Bhushan and Music by Vaishnav Kirtan. Many Bengali Singer sung the song soulfully.  Lopamudra Mitra, Bolepur Bluez, Laxman Das, Gautam Das baul, Akriti Kakar has also sung the song in their own  way.  Coke studio presents - finally Bengali Folk Song Singer Anusheh Anadil sung the song beautifully. Anusheh Anadil is sings Lalon songs, like ami opar hoye, manob jonom, milon hobe koto dine etc.



Lyrics : Tomay Hrid Majhare rakhibo chere dibona, tomay bokkho majhe rakhbo chere debona. ore chhere dile sonar gour ar pabo na , khepa chhere dile sonar gour ar pabo na na na .. ar pabona
tomay hrid majhare rakhbo , chhhere dibona


Coke Studio Bangla is youtube based music channel , we try to promote beautiful bangla music,Old Bangla songs, Bangla Folk Songs, Bangla Love Songs, Soulful Bangla Songs and Bangla New Songs 2016. Nowadays people are addicted to English and Hindi Music, that's not bad but we cant deny our own music, our own culture. So Our goal is to make you satisfied with amazing bangla music.
